==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interviewer
<hw>In"ter*view`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
interviews; especially, one who obtains an interview with another for
the purpose of eliciting his opinions or obtaining information for
publication.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It would have made him the prince of <qex>interviewers</qex> in
these days.</q> <rj><qau>Leslie Stephen.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interviewing</ent>⟦br⟧
